Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Aika! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that woman over to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go out there, you'll just end up getting caught too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait here and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured this was going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, guess they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just say "they're gone!" What do I do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:23.68,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're completely part of me, I don't want to hold back anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:28.05,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember, we got GD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:31.42,English,,0000,0000,0000,,If curiosity moves in the point of the compass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.29,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Then most likely the special power will arise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:38.55,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent city, we're salvager
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:45.27,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I will one day find the skyscraper of the submerged city
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:49.43,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid, come together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:03:00.01,English,,0000,0000,0000,,By passing through time, let's revive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:12.09,English,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things that the sun shines upon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.63,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:22.77,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to convey it to you, I don't want you to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:25.47,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I take you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:33.51,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there is a world awaiting that no one has ever seen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:36.07,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.59,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Always
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? You coming or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just close the duct after me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go! I'll go! I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, what on Earth are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultranate metal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it she isn't naked 'cause you two were having fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandra, you know something about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with their lame-ass shooting, they managed to hit something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put us down on some nearby land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Propulsion system control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disengaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separation bolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separation light, green!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue pitch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight module, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Docking procedure, start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll, pitch, yaw, dead on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Docking in seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hull latch, engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raggu engine flight module, docking completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emit Raggu energy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who are you, anyway? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, tell me! Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a spy, but you actually carry business cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is an "International Crisis Management Treaty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Authority Organization, World Secret Agent League,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Expeditionary Foreign Affairs Division" anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A class A agent, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are we going, Miss Class A Agent Meipia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Regulus' hangar bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to lose the guys after us and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, no wonder you're a class A agent! You're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet and follow me, or I'll leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did Gozo get hurt then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are all sorts of rumors about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never talks about what happened back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows the truth about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that, Aika...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Rion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rion?! What's happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing else I could do. Rescuing you was all I could manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, Aika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion... I have to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still not back to full strength. Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion... I have to save Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll do it. But first we get you strong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Food! Let's have something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you old hag! You're scaring the fish away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap, Bandra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're set on going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you're just a little kid at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "I've gotta save her" line. Just 'cause you're sweet for a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna die! Die! You're just gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I don't care! I don't care! I wanna do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Oh, yeah? Go on. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one thing, though! I'm not going with you! Do you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, don't come! I won't let you come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'll head out there myself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And keep Aika from doing anything crazy before I arrive, Bandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what your boss said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Data on the Raggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to have a debt with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmpf! I hate your type!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to see me fail like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this based off of the one that woman had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your very own, personal Ultranate metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several times more powerful than the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll wear it, won't you, Neina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suits you so well, Neina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Neina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hargen, we have a transmission from the Naval Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't wait any longer, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a formal request. Hand over the Raggu, Hargen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're prepared to use force, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That material is too valuable to give to stupid apes like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will put it to much more effective use, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, you won't get away with...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no time to listen to the chattering of apes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you destroy it, get out on your own. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meipia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabin pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oxygen regulator!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flood lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repressurization switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, Mr. Hargen's coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onboard speakers, on plus 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all crew and staff members.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is now moving into the operation's final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we reach the stratosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll hit the Earth with the Raggu Beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this operation will not result in destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raggu energy rolls back the effects of entropy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and will result in the purification of the entire Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, this operation will destroy nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the dawn of time, humanity has inflicted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,great suffering upon Mother Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now perform a ceremony for the atonement of all mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Shake a leg, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you get off of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you pulled me down here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses, glasses... Where are my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is that room from when we...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Raggu reactor, the ship's main power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight ships sighted ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In formation, with a heavy ship in the center!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound the alarm for battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raggu impingement shield, on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ships sighted blocking our course. I think it's the national fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! Raggu engines, ahead full thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! The output's rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do to stop this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy ships have opened fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take evasive action.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. I'll teach those apes a lesson they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return fire now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready all guns! Target the central ship of the formation ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plot firing solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy shots, impacting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit, forward deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy vessels, firing second salvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the main guns to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Load main guns with Raggu shells!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing solution, input!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire main guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impact in 24 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy shots, impacting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Meipia! What's with this bombardment?! I'm still on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a political decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! They're abandoning me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit, astern to port! No damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention! Our shots are impacting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Main ship, vaporized. #4 light ship, dead in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The remaining vessels are retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there it is. So, what are we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go in close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if this doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands to stations! Flight configuration!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Main wing, ready for takeoff position! Gear down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?! It just turned into a rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that thing can fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leak check. Cockpit pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabin pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air data processors?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeoff checklist, completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we reach rotation speed, engine failure will cancel takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens after takeoff, we'll perform an emergency landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Runway clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear for takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Fox, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power set, takeoff position!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, engine temp normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean, "fly"? What's gonna fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did you do? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take a look up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engine bay doors, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they stay open during take-off, they'll be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut them, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! The emergency system in the engine bay has activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't override it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One aircraft, approaching from astern!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "see you"?! What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid this is only built for one, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:21:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you! Hey! Lemme go, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'll let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You... You!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meipia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, serves her right, trying to escape by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, just let us down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gusto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.65,0:23:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Get going! It's closing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,VR!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rotation set!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.42,0:24:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop it! You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.44,0:24:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you still alive, Gusto?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.42,0:24:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:24:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.47,0:25:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.50,0:25:34.59,English,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the shining city
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.17,0:25:44.80,English,,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds were erased by the sounds of the bells and honks
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.38,0:25:50.01,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember that day's heartbeat
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.75,0:26:00.56,English,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fingertips that I felt were very sad
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.86,0:26:16.21,English,,0000,0000,0000,,If I count the stars and sigh, you overflow
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.21,0:26:24.72,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Since more strong feelings are forming little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.72,0:26:31.92,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow it's going to be a new me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.92,0:26:40.43,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I might take a detour by getting lost and by dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.43,0:26:50.47,English,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to meet your smile at my destination
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.19,0:27:11.70,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Since more strong feelings are forming little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.70,0:27:18.90,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow it's going to be a new me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.90,0:27:27.58,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I might take a detour by getting lost and by dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.58,0:27:37.25,English,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to meet your smile at my destination
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.69,0:28:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've gotten back on board Hargen's ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.59,0:28:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that Neina has been changed by the power of Ultranate metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.26,0:28:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the face of its unstoppable attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.07,0:28:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my body can only cry out in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.00,0:28:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You want to beg me for your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.64,0:28:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Hargen's terrifying project begins to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.57,0:28:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the aim of recreating the greatest earthquake in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.94,0:28:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the ideal of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.61,0:28:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll create a utopia!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.55,0:28:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! You can't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.22,0:28:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, next trial:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.99,0:28:49.91,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,322)}A Flower Blooming in Space
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.22,0:28:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Flower Blooming in Space"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.96,0:28:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shining aurora leads the way to destruction.
